    "content": "\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 mt-6\">🏛 정치 주요 뉴스</h2>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-8\">\n  <table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-100\">\n        <th class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-center w-8\">#</th>\n        <th class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-left\">헤드라인</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">1</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">1·2번 정치에 갇힌 한국, 피로와 냉소만 남아<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">뉴스클레임</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-50\">\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">2</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">[뉴스룸에서] 한국 정치의 또 다른 세습<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">v.daum.net</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">3</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">국민의힘 경북도지사 예비경선, 김재원 승리…이철우 지사와 '한국시리즈' 본격화 \"<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">영주인터넷방송</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-50\">\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">4</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">김 총리 '김대중 대통령은 한국 정치 교과서…민주주의 꽃 피워'<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">뉴스통</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">5</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">이재명 대통령 부부, 2026 한국교회 부활절 연합예배 참석<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">중부뉴스통신</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 mt-6\">💰 경제 주요 뉴스</h2>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-8\">\n  <table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-100\">\n        <th class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-center w-8\">#</th>\n        <th class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-left\">헤드라인</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">1</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">\"한국에 최우선 공급하겠다\"…중동 6개국 '깜짝 선언'<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">v.daum.net</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-50\">\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">2</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">\"삼성전자 내일 50조 터진다\"…상위 1% 투자 고수들 '싹쓸이' [마켓PRO]<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">한국경제</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">3</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">강훈식 \"오늘 카자흐·오만·사우디로 출국…원유 확보 협의\"<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">한국경제</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-50\">\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">4</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">조선일보, 영업이익 1위 했지만…중앙일보·한국경제에 매출 역전 당해<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">미디어오늘</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 text-center w-8\">5</td>\n        <td class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2\">“한국 경제는 유가보다 반도체 수출이 결정”<span class=\"text-slate-400 text-xs ml-2\">조선일보</span></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 mt-6\">📰 사회 주요 뉴스</h2>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-8\">\n  <table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr class=\"bg-slate-100\">\n        <th class=\"border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-center w-8\">#</th>\n        <th class=\"border b